## Editing overrides

- Prefer **`BJIntrusive_PUSH` / `BJIntrusive_POP` / `BJIntrusive_MESSAGE`** (1.91 file). Older overrides still use `BOOST_PATH_PUSH` / `BOOST_MESSAGE`; wire those to `BJIntrusive_*` in `intrusivedebug.h` if path tracking must work on older Boost.
- Keep each override byte-identical to upstream except the marked intrusive blocks — eases rebasing on Boost upgrades.
- New override file → add `#elif` in `intrusivedebug.h` and document in this rule.
